    public static enum TStream.Routing

    Enumeration for routing tuples to parallel channels.
    See Also:
    TStream.parallel(int, Routing)

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      PARTITIONED
      Tuples will be consistenly routed to the same channel based upon their value.
      ROUND_ROBIN
      Tuples will be routed to parallel channels such that an even distribution is maintained.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • ROUND_ROBIN

        public static final TStream.Routing ROUND_ROBIN
        Tuples will be routed to parallel channels such that an even distribution is maintained.

      • PARTITIONED

        public static final TStream.Routing PARTITIONED
        Tuples will be consistenly routed to the same channel based upon their value.

        If the tuple implements the Keyable interface, then the tuple is routed to a parallel channel according to the hashCode() of the object returned by Keyable.getKey(). If the tuple does not implement the Keyable interface, then the tuple is routed to a parallel channel according to the hashCode() of the tuple object itself.
